{"id": "1209393586089492500", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "type": 19, "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "author_bot": false, "content": "Yes you do. Every single material used. Infact the material is left in inventory for you to pick the material you want it to be. What I mean is, you'll get a general box for each tier of material used in such a way that you can select which material comes out for either RED, YELLOW characters etc.", "timestamp": "2024-02-20T06:58:20.370000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["391357465687752714"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1209381990395154522", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1209393787177013280", "channel_id": "1170692781216378960", "type": 19, "author_id": "543093645947961348", "author_name": "turboseer", "author_bot": false, "content": "It does, but there's only 2. One returns everything but leaves the character.\nThe other returns everything and deletes the character.", "timestamp": "2024-02-20T06:59:08.313000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["865104013191938049"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1209393513603665952", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
